typeProperties.script:
section Section1;
shared src_blob_csv_rpt_emulate = let
  AdfDoc = AzureStorage.BlobContents("https://chianti.blob.core.windows.net/report-emulate/train.csv"),
  Csv = Csv.Document(AdfDoc, [Delimiter = "", Encoding = TextEncoding.Utf8, QuoteStyle = QuoteStyle.Csv]),
  PromotedHeaders = Table.PromoteHeaders(Csv, [PromoteAllScalars = true])
in
  PromotedHeaders;
shared UserQuery = let
  Source = src_blob_csv_rpt_emulate
in
  Source;
